    "body": "Thanks for pinging me. \r\nI think that make sens for consistency. It would be relatively easy to add a configuration option to change the behavior. \r\n\r\nWould that be ok only for the next major version ? \r\n\r\nNote that it should be relatively easy to backport as a custom package/extension for IPYthon, where you can just overwrite magics, if you want to have it on earlier versions. "
